HEADWORD: Telephonic
<hw>Tel`e*phon"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>t⟦eacute⟧l⟦eacute⟧phonique</ets>. See <er>Telephone</er>.]</ety>
